•	Freehold sale over one title
•	Existing building of 4,897 sqm*

•	Ability to divide into multiple tenancies (STCA)
•	Low office component

For further information, to obtain a copy of the contract or to arrange an inspection of this exceptional opportunity please contact the exclusive selling agents CBRE.

Bdg 2, Keylink Industrial Estate (Nth), 395 Pembroke Road

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer a sublease opportunity at Building 2 at Keylink Industrial Estate (North), 395 Pembroke Road, Minto.

The estate is centrally connected to major arterial roads and a short distance to Leumeah Train station. This estate is positioned adjacent to the Macarthur Intermodal Shipping Terminal (MIST) making it ideal for occupiers with high volume of container movements.

Features include;
- 8,030sqm* warehouse & 202sqm* office space
- Internal clearance 9.4-11.5m
- Access via two recessed docks and four on-grade roller shutters
- Awning for all-weather loading
- ESFR sprinklered
- Separate car and truck access
- Stand-alone warehouse facility 
- 4kms* to the Hume Highway
- 13kms* M5 & M7 Motorways
- 600m* to Minto Marketplace

For further information please contact the CBRE exclusively listed agents.
